---
import BaseLayout from '../layouts/BaseLayout.astro';
---

<BaseLayout
  title="Affiliate Disclosure"
  description="How affiliate partnerships work on this site."
>
  <main class="legal-page">
    <div class="legal-container">
      <h1>Affiliate Disclosure</h1>
      <p class="last-updated">Last updated: March 9, 2026</p>
      <p>This site is part of the <a href="https://discovermore.travel">Discover More</a> travel network. We participate in affiliate programs, which means we may earn a commission when you book hotels, tours, activities, or purchase products through links on our site — at no extra cost to you.</p>
      <h2>Our Partners</h2>
      <ul>
        <li>Booking.com — hotels and accommodations</li>
        <li>Agoda — hotels (Asia focus)</li>
        <li>GetYourGuide — tours and activities</li>
        <li>Klook — tours, activities, and transport</li>
        <li>Viator — tours and experiences</li>
        <li>Hotels.com — hotels and accommodations</li>
        <li>12Go Asia — ferries, buses, and trains</li>
        <li>SafetyWing — travel insurance</li>
        <li>Amazon — travel gear and packing essentials</li>
      </ul>
      <h2>Our Promise</h2>
      <p>Every recommendation on this site passes the <strong>"Would I recommend this if there were zero commission?"</strong> test.</p>
      <p>Affiliate partnerships help us keep this site free and ad-free while continuing to create in-depth travel content.</p>
      <h2>FTC Compliance</h2>
      <p>In accordance with the Federal Trade Commission's guidelines on endorsements and testimonials (16 CFR Part 255), this disclosure is provided to ensure full transparency about our affiliate relationships.</p>
      <h2>Questions?</h2>
      <p>Email <strong>info@discovermore.travel</strong></p>
    </div>
  </main>
</BaseLayout>
<style>
  .legal-page { max-width: 800px; margin: 0 auto; padding: 2rem 1.5rem 4rem; }
  .legal-container h1 { margin-bottom: 0.5rem; }
  .last-updated { color: var(--text-mid, #888); font-size: 0.9rem; margin-bottom: 2rem; }
  .legal-container h2 { margin-top: 2rem; margin-bottom: 0.75rem; }
  .legal-container ul { margin-bottom: 1rem; padding-left: 1.5rem; }
  .legal-container li { margin-bottom: 0.5rem; line-height: 1.6; }
  .legal-container p { line-height: 1.6; margin-bottom: 1rem; }
  .legal-container a { color: var(--teal, #0D7377); }
</style>
